      "description": "Hub map of the entire Powerhouse knowledge graph — architecture, design systems, platforms, and organization",
      "orientation": "The Powerhouse ecosystem spans three interconnected domains. The technical foundation (Reactor, Document Models, CQRS, GraphQL) provides the storage and processing layer. The design systems (brand identity, color tokens, theming) define how products look and feel across Achra, Vetra, and the Powerhouse parent brand. The organizational layer (SNO structure, open-source capitalism, platform strategy) governs how the network coordinates people, code, and capital. This hub connects all 17 domain and topic MOCs into a single navigable entry point.",
